## Success Criteria

- Trello json is periodically backed up
- backups occur without manual trigger
- json & keys stored securely; accessible by a few other members of the group (github + trello accounts for [info@clackamasdsa.org](mailto:info@clackamasdsa.org "‌")?)
- steps for board restoration from json are documented clearly
- backups occur on ~1x/month basis

## Implementation

Github Actions for execution + repo for storage

[scheduled Github Actions](https://docs.github.com/en/actions/using-workflows/events-that-trigger-workflows#schedule "‌")

## Details

**Date**: Wednesday, May 24, 9 a.m.–12:30 p.m.

**Location**: Portland Building 1120 SW 5th Ave., Room 206

**From OPAL**: “The May meeting will be more of an ‘in-person demonstration and vote disruption event.’ Arrival time is 8:30.”
